+- Keep Python annotations on function definitions or assignments only; never splice annotations into ternary expressions or return expressions.
+- Before returning a proposal, mentally validate that every edited Python file can pass `py_compile` and every edited TypeScript file is syntactically complete.
 
-- edit the smallest possible file set, preferably one implementation file and one focused test file;
